00:00:12,020 --> 00:00:15,500
=Episode 20=

3
00:00:15,720 --> 00:00:16,510
Si,

4
00:00:17,120 --> 00:00:18,920
are you making it hard for me?

5
00:00:19,320 --> 00:00:20,190
I don't dare to.

6
00:00:20,670 --> 00:00:22,440
Si, no need to get all tense.

7
00:00:22,440 --> 00:00:24,920
The search is also to prove his innocence.

8
00:00:25,510 --> 00:00:27,190
I do have a packet of poison on me.

9
00:00:32,150 --> 00:00:34,000
It's called Qianji poison.

10
00:00:34,110 --> 00:00:35,200
But this poison

11
00:00:36,880 --> 00:00:38,710
was given to me
by a servant of the State Counselor.

12
00:00:39,320 --> 00:00:40,430
Nonsense.

13
00:00:41,070 --> 00:00:42,840
I'm the State Counselor of Donglan,

14
00:00:43,110 --> 00:00:45,350
why would I give you poison for no reason?

15
00:00:45,350 --> 00:00:47,320
Because you want to murder Her Majesty.

16
00:00:47,790 --> 00:00:48,600
You...

17
00:00:51,520 --> 00:00:52,320
Your Majesty,

18
00:00:53,240 --> 00:00:54,000
a few days ago,

19
00:00:54,710 --> 00:00:56,240
the State Counselor
came to me for cooperation,

20
00:00:56,470 --> 00:00:57,470
wanting to assassinate you.

21
00:00:57,920 --> 00:00:59,320
He promised me that when he gets the throne,

22
00:01:00,070 --> 00:01:01,110
he would support me

23
00:01:01,280 --> 00:01:02,320
to be the King of Xiling.

24
00:01:03,240 --> 00:01:03,960
State Counselor,

25
00:01:04,120 --> 00:01:05,310
is that true?

26
00:01:07,070 --> 00:01:08,230
Your Majesty,

27
00:01:08,230 --> 00:01:09,920
I'm loyal to Your Majesty,

28
00:01:09,920 --> 00:01:12,230
and I'm faithful to Donglan,
I have no second thoughts.

29
00:01:12,280 --> 00:01:14,710
Since he said my servant gave him the poison,

30
00:01:15,310 --> 00:01:16,710
let them confront each other face to face.

31
00:01:20,760 --> 00:01:21,710
Your Majesty,

32
00:01:21,840 --> 00:01:23,790
a body has been found
near the Princess's residence.

33
00:01:24,120 --> 00:01:25,350
This was found

34
00:01:25,350 --> 00:01:26,400
on the dead man's body.

35
00:01:31,580 --> 00:01:32,700
(Token)

36
00:01:35,120 --> 00:01:36,840
The token of the spy of Xiling.

37
00:01:39,280 --> 00:01:41,480
Is there really a spy?

38
00:01:42,150 --> 00:01:43,120
Your Majesty,

39
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:45,510
this man is not
the real Seventh Prince of Xiling,

40
00:01:46,070 --> 00:01:48,480
he's a spy planted in Donglan by Xiling.

41
00:01:48,480 --> 00:01:50,710
He used to lurk in the Phoenix Academy,

42
00:01:50,950 --> 00:01:53,070
but now he lurks beside the Princess.

43
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:55,510
This man is evil and ambitious
and he's up to no good.

44
00:01:55,510 --> 00:01:56,710
We must eliminate him.

45
00:01:56,710 --> 00:01:57,640
You're lying.

46
00:01:58,040 --> 00:01:58,710
State Counselor,

47
00:01:58,920 --> 00:02:00,310
it's not an accusation made out of nothing.

48
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:01,640
Do you have any proof?

49
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:15,470
Search it.

50
00:02:15,470 --> 00:02:16,120
Yes.

51
00:02:23,020 --> 00:02:23,940
(Yu eyes only)

52
00:02:32,820 --> 00:02:33,900
(Yu eyes only)

53
00:02:35,220 --> 00:02:38,300
(Yu eyes only)

54
00:02:42,980 --> 00:02:46,340
(King of Xiling)

55
00:02:48,910 --> 00:02:50,630
Look at this, Si.

56
00:02:50,710 --> 00:02:53,120
Not only does it have
the handwriting of the King of Xiling,

57
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:54,430
it also has the Seal of Xiling.

58
00:02:54,710 --> 00:02:56,000
How can this be fake?

59
00:02:56,340 --> 00:02:57,500
(King of Xiling)

60
00:02:59,240 --> 00:03:00,590
Mother, it's...

61
00:03:01,310 --> 00:03:02,360
Your Majesty,

62
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:04,430
a few days ago, I observed the sky at night.

63
00:03:04,430 --> 00:03:06,240
I saw that the Zi Wei star
was shining brightly,

64
00:03:06,240 --> 00:03:08,120
but suddenly
there was a fatal star beside it.

65
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:10,120
It's an ominous sign
that the head of state will be in trouble.

66
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:12,280
Who knew it would come true now?

67
00:03:12,310 --> 00:03:13,520
I have to be bold

68
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:16,120
to ask Your Majesty
to kill this man without mercy.

69
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:17,710
Guards,

70
00:03:18,190 --> 00:03:18,910
take him down.

71
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:19,870
Wait.

72
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:22,430
Mother, Father,

73
00:03:22,630 --> 00:03:24,310
I don't believe he's a spy.

74
00:03:24,470 --> 00:03:25,360
I beg you, Mother,

75
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:27,280
don't listen to
the one-sided words of a trickster,

76
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:28,400
find out the truth.

77
00:03:28,750 --> 00:03:29,560
Si,

78
00:03:29,710 --> 00:03:31,080
don't be silly.

79
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:33,080
No. This man is dangerous.

80
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:36,120
Princess, you're delicate and priceless,

81
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:37,870
