82
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:40,190
Your Majesty,

83
00:03:41,030 --> 00:03:42,840
Si is so insistent,

84
00:03:42,870 --> 00:03:44,400
she must have her reasons.

85
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:45,630
How about this?

86
00:03:45,840 --> 00:03:47,280
Tie this man up

87
00:03:47,430 --> 00:03:48,590
and give him to Si

88
00:03:48,590 --> 00:03:49,680
for a night's interrogation.

89
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:51,080
It wouldn't be a bad idea.

90
00:03:53,310 --> 00:03:54,120
Mother,

91
00:03:54,310 --> 00:03:56,470
