92
00:03:56,960 --> 00:03:58,030
I just want to find out

93
00:03:58,030 --> 00:04:00,240
if I made the right choice or not.

94
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:06,400
Si, I hope you know

95
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:07,910
