96
00:04:08,310 --> 00:04:09,280
Don't worry,

97
00:04:09,470 --> 00:04:10,630
I'll do what I say.

98
00:04:10,870 --> 00:04:12,680
If he is really a spy,

99
00:04:12,710 --> 00:04:14,310
I'll kill him myself

100
